<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Airtel Thanks App - Quality Digital Services</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
  <style>
  * {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}

body {
  background-color: #f2f4ff;
  padding: 20px;
}

.header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background-color: white;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: bold;
}
.logo img {
  width: 300px;
  height: 80px;
}

.logo .highlight {
  color: #f57c00;
}

.nav-links a {
  margin: 0 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #f57c00;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.main-container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 30px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.info-card {
  flex: 2;
  background-color: #e8f1ff;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.info-card h2 {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: #c60000;
}

.info-card h3 {
  margin-top: 20px;
  color: #333;
}

.info-card ul, .info-card ol {
  padding-left: 20px;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.app-logo {
  width: 60px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.form-card {
  flex: 1;
  background-color: white;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.form-card h2 {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

form {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

label {
  margin: 10px 0 5px;
  font-weight: bold;
}

input, select {
  padding: 10px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  border: 1px solid #aaa;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

button {
  padding: 12px;
  background-color: #f57c00;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
  font-weight: bold;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.3s;
}

button:hover {
  background-color: #e06b00;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="image/Hiring_Poster1Artboard_8@4x[1](1).png"></div>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="/dashboard">Home</a>
      <a href="/aboutneed">About Us</a>
      <a href="/careerneed">Careers</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="main-container">
    <section class="info-card">
      <img src="image/HDFC Rupay Credit Card.png" alt="Airtel Logo" class="app-logo"/>
      <h2>IRCTC HDFC Bank Credit Card – Key Highlights
Promoted by Quality Digital Services</h2>
      <h3>Benefits:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>🚆 5 Reward Points per ₹100 spent on IRCTC ticket bookings</li>
        <li>💳 1 Reward Point per ₹100 spent on all other purchases</li>
        <li>💰 5% Extra Cashback on train tickets via HDFC SmartBuy</li>
        <li>🛋 8 Complimentary Lounge Accesses per year (2 per quarter) at select IRCTC Executive Lounges</li>
        <li>🎁 ₹500 Gift Voucher on quarterly spends of ₹30,000</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Whom to Promote? (Eligibility):</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>🎂 Age: 21 to 60 years</li>
        <li>👔 Salaried: Minimum ₹18,000 monthly income</li>
        <li>🧾 Self-Employed: Minimum ₹6 LPA (ITR)</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>How It Works:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Visit the credit card application portal</li>
        <li>Search for ‘IRCTC HDFC Bank Credit Card’</li>
        <li>Click on ‘Apply Now’</li>
        <li>Enter your registered mobile number and verify with OTP</li>
        <li>Fill in the required details (PAN, income, etc.)</li>
        <li>Upload the documents and submit your application</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Terms & Conditions:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Reward Points & Cashback are category-specific.</li>
        <li>Lounge access limited to 2 visits per quarter.</li>
        <li>Rewards and earning rates may change at any time without prior notice</li>
        <li>A referral bonus of flat *2% earnings* applies.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

   
  </main>
<br><br>
  <button style="margin-left: 50%;">click here to Continue</button>
  
</body>
</html>
